</head>
<body>
  <div class="cover-card">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529626455594-4ff0802cfb7e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=720&h=1280&q=80" alt="9:16 strip">
  </div>
</body>
</html>

Option C (keep cover but choose the visible part)
